plham

Class OrderBook

  • plham.OrderBook

  • public class OrderBook
    A class for orderbooks for continuous double action mechanism. Orders are arranged in the price/time priority basis. Use HIGHERS_FIRST for buy side; Use LOWERS_FIRST for sell side.
